{{单双书号转换|'''枕邊情話'''}}（{{lang-en|"Pillowtalk"}}）是英国歌手[[泽恩·马利克|泽恩]]於2015年3月25日退出[[1世代|1世代]]後的個人歌手出道作品，收录于他的第一张个人录音室专辑《{{Le|心解密|Mind of Mine}}》（{{lang|en|''Mind of Mine''}}）中。歌曲于2016年1月29日作为专辑的首张单曲与歌曲的音乐录影带一同发布。2月2日，歌曲被发送到当代流行电台播出。

《枕邊情話》在发行后获得了主流乐评人的好评，乐评大都称赞了泽恩的全新音乐方向和人声表现。歌曲的音樂錄影帶使用了万花筒式效果，美国模特[[吉吉·哈蒂德|吉吉·哈蒂德]]参与了錄影帶的演出。

歌曲获得了一定的商业成功，在超过12个国家的单曲榜夺得冠军，包括[[英國單曲排行榜|英國單曲排行榜]]和美国[[告示牌百强单曲榜|告示牌百强单曲榜]]。其中，歌曲是美国第25首空降冠军的歌曲。

== 背景和发行 ==
在离开[[1世代|1世代]]组合后，泽恩跟[[RCA唱片|RCA唱片]]签下合约<ref>{{cite news|last1=Strecker|first1=Erin|title=Zayn Malik Signs With RCA, Tweets Excitement|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6648505/zayn-malik-signs-rca|access-date=29 July 2015|work=[[Billboard_(magazine)|Billboard]]|agency=[[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]]|date=29 July 2015|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6aSU2QMs5?url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6648505/zayn-malik-signs-rca|archive-date=1 August 2015|location=United States|url-status=dead}}</ref>，开始个人演唱事业。他向音乐杂志透露他首张个人作品将会在音乐上偏向[[节奏布鲁斯|节奏布鲁斯]]，但一些旋律也会靠近节奏布鲁斯-摇滚或者雷鬼。<ref>{{cite web|title=Zayn Malik's Next Direction|url=http://www.thefader.com/2015/11/17/zayn-malik-fader-cover-story-interview-solo-album-one-direction|access-date=8 January 2016|author=Cooper, Duncan|date=17 November 2015|work=The Fader|archive-date=2016-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107014718/http://www.thefader.com/2015/11/17/zayn-malik-fader-cover-story-interview-solo-album-one-direction|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年1月24日，首支单曲《枕边情话》的名称和发行日由泽恩在Twitter宣布<ref>{{Cite web|title=Zayn Malik Announces Release Date for First Single ‘Pillowtalk’|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/pop/zayn-malik-pillowtalk-single-release-date-6851719/|access-date=2021-11-28|date=2016-01-24|last=Strecker|first=Erin|work=Billboard|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211128102037/https://www.billboard.com/music/pop/zayn-malik-pillowtalk-single-release-date-6851719/|dead-url=no}}</ref>；在他与前任未婚妻，[[混合甜心|混合甜心]]组合成员{{Le|佩莉·爱德华兹|Perrie Edwards}}分手之后，泽恩从中找到灵感<ref>{{cite web|title=Zayn Malik's 'Pillowtalk': How Perrie Edwards Feels About The Video She Inspired|url=http://hollywoodlife.com/2016/01/29/perrie-edwards-reaction-zayn-malik-pillowtalk-gigi-hadid-video-dating/|access-date=21 September 2016|date=29 January 2016|last=LaCroix|first=Emy|publisher=Hollywood Life|archive-date=2021-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222061820/https://hollywoodlife.com/2016/01/29/perrie-edwards-reaction-zayn-malik-pillowtalk-gigi-hadid-video-dating/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，与词曲作家麦克尔和安东尼·汉尼德斯一同写下这首歌。泽恩对《[[星期日泰晤士報|星期日泰晤士报]]》描述这首歌有关于性爱；他将性爱形容为“好纯洁，好肮脏，好原始”。

歌曲和音乐录影带于29日全球发行<ref name="release">{{cite web|title=Zayn Malik's Sexy 'Pillowtalk' Video is Here: Watch|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6859197/zayn-malik-pillowtalk-video-released|access-date=29 January 2016|author=Billboard Staff|date=29 January 2016|work=Billboard|archive-date=2019-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190104080946/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6859197/zayn-malik-pillowtalk-video-released|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并登上全球多个音乐排行榜榜首。根据[[國際唱片業協會|国际唱片业协会]]的统计，这首歌曲全球等价销量已达到8百万张。

== 评论 ==
休·麦金太尔在《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》杂志上写道，“毋庸置疑，（这首歌曲）是相当成熟的，用不少十八禁词汇描述出了成人向的影像和主题。这不止是一首关于失恋的平庸作品；这首歌说的是爱情同时作为享乐天堂和激烈战场的两种形态。即使这首歌里面的情境会似曾相识，但是泽恩的感受和表达跟以前都不一样了。<ref name="forbes">{{cite web|title=Zayn Malik Releases 'Pillowtalk', His First Single Since Leaving One Direction|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/hughmcintyre/2016/01/29/zayn-malik-releases-pillowtalk-his-first-single-since-leaving-one-direction/#738157c87a7c|access-date=29 January 2016|author=McIntyre, Hugh|work=Forbes|archive-date=2021-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211128100925/https://www.forbes.com/sites/hughmcintyre/2016/01/29/zayn-malik-releases-pillowtalk-his-first-single-since-leaving-one-direction/#738157c87a7c|dead-url=no}}</ref>”《{{Internal link helper/en|Fuse (电视频道)|Fuse (TV channel)|Fuse}}》频道的Jason Lipshutz评论这首歌曲是“一首性感的、让人着迷的节奏布鲁斯曲目”。<ref>{{cite web|title=Zayn Malik Makes Solo Debut: Listen to PILLOWTALK|url=http://www.fuse.tv/2016/01/zayn-malik-pillowtalk-single-video-listen|access-date=29 January 2016|author=Lipshutz, Jason|date=29 January 2016|work=Fuse|archive-date=2021-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211128100058/https://www.fuse.tv/2016/01/zayn-malik-pillowtalk-single-video-listen|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[Spin_(雜誌)|Spin]]》杂志的Brennan Carley积极评价了歌曲的歌词以及泽恩的声乐表现，说他“分秒之间证明了他对现代节奏布鲁斯的掌控力。他的声音充满了激情，离团让他的声线得以自由原始地发挥。”<ref name="spin">{{cite web|title=Zayn Malik's 'Pillowtalk' Proves Leaving One Direction Was the Right Move|url=http://www.spin.com/2016/01/zayn-malik-pillowtalk-new-single-solo-one-direction/|access-date=29 January 2016|author=Carley, Brennan|date=29 January 2016|work=Spin|archive-date=2021-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211128100925/https://www.spin.com/2016/01/zayn-malik-pillowtalk-new-single-solo-one-direction/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[衛報|卫报]]》把歌曲评为一周最佳；该报的Harriet Gibsone写道，“这首歌是：缓慢、简约、激昂的荷尔蒙爆炸，香槟酒喷泉，差劲的须后水。这是他主动而为的 - 也合乎情理的 - 向更严肃的艺术表象的迈出的一步。”<ref name="the guardian">{{cite web|title=Zayn Malik's Pillowtalk: sex, hugs and sobbing blood|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2016/jan/29/zayn-malik-pillowtalk-first-track-listen|access-date=29 January 2016|author=Gibsone, Harriet|date=29 January 2016|work=The Guardian|archive-date=2021-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211128100059/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2016/jan/29/zayn-malik-pillowtalk-first-track-listen|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[爱尔兰时报|爱尔兰时报]]》也把歌曲选为周度精选曲目，并评论说歌曲是“丝滑”的“新派节奏布鲁斯”，并和歌手{{Le|米格尔 (歌手)|Miguel (singer)|米格尔}}作比。

在《Stereogum》的乐评中，Tom Breihan称其为“丝滑、整齐构建的情绪之作”。<ref>{{cite web|title=Zayn – "Pillowtalk" Video|url=http://www.stereogum.com/1856095/zayn-pillowtalk/mp3s/|access-date=9 February 2016|date=29 January 2015|work=Stereogum|archive-date=2020-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201012010458/https://www.stereogum.com/1856095/zayn-pillowtalk/mp3s/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在写给《[[數碼間諜|數碼間諜]]》的乐评中，Lewis Corner将这首“魅惑的节奏布鲁斯”曲目跟[[威肯|威肯]]的声音和[[賈斯汀·提姆布萊克|贾斯汀·汀布莱克]]早期个人作品比较，给出四星评分（满分五星），并总结说，这不是“陈旧无聊的流行垃圾”，而是“让你始料未及的下一代英国男歌手超级巨星”；他评论说，“泽恩的清晰声线在这首歌曲中发挥到了最好，加上宏大的副歌和抓耳的旋律，让这首歌性感、有趣又不失风度。”<ref name="digitalspy">{{cite web|title=Why Zayn Malik is more Justin Timberlake than Robbie Williams: 'Pillowtalk' first single review|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/music/single-reviews/review/a781569/why-zayn-is-more-justin-timberlake-than-robbie-williams-pillowtalk-first-single-review/|access-date=29 January 2016|author=Corner, Lewis|date=29 January 2016|work=Digital Spy|archive-date=2018-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181102065531/http://www.digitalspy.com/music/single-reviews/review/a781569/why-zayn-is-more-justin-timberlake-than-robbie-williams-pillowtalk-first-single-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

